NAME: Affymetrix other
DESCRIPTION: Other Affymetrix file formats (DAT, RPT, and TXT formats).

NAME: Converted FCS file
DESCRIPTION: FCS file converted for FLOW analysis.

NAME: FASTQ
DESCRIPTION: FASTQ- sequencing read data file format for combining the sequence and per base quality score.

NAME: FPKM
DESCRIPTION: Fragments Per Kilobase Of Exon Per Million Fragments- Measurement of mRNA abundance using RNA-seq data.

NAME: Flow cytometry result in text format
DESCRIPTION: Flow cytometer or analysis software output in text format.

NAME: Illumina GA
DESCRIPTION: Illumina Genome Analyzer sequencer non-normalized result.

NAME: MBAA result
DESCRIPTION: Multiplex Bead Array Assay. bead level result are the primary output of MBBA instruments.

NAME: Markers or channels description
DESCRIPTION: Description of marker or channels in a FCS file.

NAME: RPKM
DESCRIPTION: Reads Per Kilobase per Million reads- Measurement of mRNA abundance using RNA-seq data.

NAME: TPM
DESCRIPTION: Transcripts per million reads- Measurement of mRNA abundance using RNA-seq data.

NAME: Archived
DESCRIPTION: Files stored and not linked to result data.

NAME: Flow cytometry compensation or control
DESCRIPTION: Flow cytometry compensation or control files.

NAME: ImmPort BDC file
DESCRIPTION: ImmPort defined file format for database updates.

NAME: Gene expression result
DESCRIPTION: Measurement values from  Gene expression assays.
